    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Boundary Condition is an award-winning puzzle-platformer that explores the physics of cross-sections.  In each level, you may need to flatten into 2D or 1D in order to bypass obstacles.  Squeeze through narrow gaps, climb steep slopes, and cross wide chasms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141790/extras/d48ea31bb639a97472fb95dfaf12a524.poster.avif?t=1770926584\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141790/extras/d48ea31bb639a97472fb95dfaf12a524.webm?t=1770926584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141790/extras/d48ea31bb639a97472fb95dfaf12a524.mp4?t=1770926584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141790/extras/3297ea755894e58b09e5e297a27c0f62.poster.avif?t=1770926584\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141790/extras/3297ea755894e58b09e5e297a27c0f62.webm?t=1770926584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141790/extras/3297ea755894e58b09e5e297a27c0f62.mp4?t=1770926584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between the levels, discover the philosophical writings of a  programmer who is working on a complex project involving a mysterious machine.  The sunk cost continues to sink deeper, but surely she'll find a way to pull it together in the end, right? . . . Right?</p>",
